'''''Toxicon''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] of [[toxinology]] and the official journal of the [[International Society on Toxinology]]. It is published by [[Elsevier]] and the [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Alan L. Harvey]]. It aims to publish [[original research]], novel findings, and [[review journal|review papers]] on [[toxin]]s and their [[chemistry|chemical]], [[toxicology|toxicological]], [[pharmacology|pharmacological]], and [[immunology|immunological properties]].

The journal was established in 1962. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', it received a 2011 [[impact factor]] of 2.508, ranking it 36th out of 83 journals in the category "Toxicology"<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2012 |chapter=Journals Ranked by Impact: Toxicology |title=2011 Journal Citation Reports |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition= Sciences |accessdate= |work=Web of Science |postscript=.}}</ref> and 109th out of 261 journals in the category "Pharmacology & Pharmacy".<ref name=WoS1>{{cite book |year=2012 |chapter=Journals Ranked by Impact: Pharmacology & Pharmacy |title=2011 Journal Citation Reports |publisher=Thomson Reuters |edition= Sciences |accessdate= |work=Web of Science |postscript=.}}</ref>

